7 different games are played: billiard, go, mah-jongg, monopoly, scrabble, domino, bridge
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, trike, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person playing bridge##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person playing billiard##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
14. the person driving the van is the person drinking water##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
