 4. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating apricot is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person eating lime##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating lime##1
11. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the analyst is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
15. the person eating lime is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
