.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, quad-bike, van, trike, ship, roller
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 3. the person driving the bus is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person driving the bus is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person driving the bus is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the writer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Transport   | roller | quad-bike        | ship    | trike     | van     | skateboard   | bus        |
| Pet           | bird   | ferret       | mouse    | guinea-pig | hedgehog | snake   | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, cooking, dancing, gardening, hiking, photography, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard, rat, turtle
City: nizza, london, rome, boston, colone, paris, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is baking##2
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the rat##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the person traveling to nizza##1
15. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Hobby       | dancing  | photography | gardening  | woodworking | cooking | hiking | baking |
| Pet         | hedgehog | goldfish    | dog        | lizard      | rat     | frog   | turtle |
| City   | rome  | london   | colone | paris        | boston    | hamburg  | nizza   |

