.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, punk, trance, classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
7 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, hamster, hedgehog, horse, mouse, pony
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, biathlon, cycling, rowing, surfing, volleyball
 1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's sport is rowing##2
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the fan of punk is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the fan of funk is in the middle##1
13. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
14. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |     7      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | punk    | dubstep  | funk        | indie | trance | classical     |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | hedgehog | pony     | mouse      | horse     | fish     | hamster    |
| Sport         | baseball   | surfing  | biathlon | basketball | rowing    | cycling  | volleyball |

