.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-19::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, bartender, dancer, firefighter, mechanic, photographer, videographer
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, crime, disaster, documentary, drama, satire, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, pop, funk, salsa, punk, soul
 1. the firefighter is on the left of the videographer##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the photographer is the fan of soul##1
 6. the videographer is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left of the bartender##1
12. the fan of reggae is between the dancer and the fan of punk##2
13. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is the fan of punk##1
15. the accountant is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |      5       |      6      |      7       |
| Job           | dancer      | accountant | mechanic | bartender   | photographer | firefighter | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | disaster   | action   | documentary | crime        | drama       | satire       |
| Music-Genre         | ambient    | reggae       | punk   | funk      | soul   | pop  | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, coral, azure, ebony, mauve, green
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, gardening, photography, skydiving, traveling, writing
7 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, snake
 1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes azure##1
 7. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the owner of the frog##2
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the owner of the snake and the person who's hobby is writing##2
15. the owner of the snake is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Color   | green  | mauve   | ebony   | azure        | coral     | aquamarine | blood-red       |
| Hobby      | dancing | filmmaking | writing | photography | gardening  | skydiving   | traveling |
| Pet        | snake   | ferret     | cat     | lizard      | guinea-pig | goldfish    | frog      |

 